ActOther Than Statutory Authority
SubjectMoosomin Indian Reserve No. 112K (Saskatchewan)
PrecisOrder amending Order in Council P.C. 2005-2295 dated December 6, 2005 regarding MOOSOMIN INDIAN RESERVE No. 112K, in Saskatchewan, to clarify that the lands were to be set apart as a new reserve and not as an addition to the reserve.
